import numpy as np

def cross_product(v1, v2):
    v1 = np.array(v1)
    v2 = np.array(v2)
    cross = np.cross(v1, v2)
    mag = np.linalg.norm(cross)
    if mag < 5:
        cross = cross * (5 / mag)
    return cross
